text: Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. is an American TV series and the first series of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU). The series was created by Joss Whedon, Jed Whedon, and Maurissa Tancharoen and was on ABC from September 24, 2013 to August 12, 2020. Clark Gregg stars in the series, returning as Phil Coulson from the MCU movies.
